<div class="end-user container mt-4">
  <h2 class="end-user__tittle text-center">本当に退会しますか？</h2>
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="post-blog__form col-sm-8 text-center">
      <p>
        退会すると、会員登録情報や<br>
